	    \quad\text{and}\quad
	    g \colon \left\{x \in \R \;\middle\vert\; x \neq 0,\, 2\right\} \to \R</me>
	    defined by
	    <me>f(x) = \frac{x + 1}{x(x-1)}
	    \quad\text{and}\quad
	    g(x) = \frac{x - 4}{x(x-2)}.</me>	
	  </p>
	</introduction>
